@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cetwiz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.69)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v2 + 0.16 * v1 + 0.66)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos(0.07))
    v2 = (wp.exp(v2) * ((v1 + 0.53 + v2 + 0.60) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.98)))
    data[tid] = v0
